{
  "texts": [
    "For LDA and Top2Vec, we used noun-only POS filtering for 5 topics since 5 topics is the average number of flat topics obtained from community mining.",
    "We did not need to tune any hyperparameters for the Top2Vec algorithm.",
    "To run BERTopic, we provided the raw text corpus to the model and set the verbose flag to True, which helped to track the stages of the model.",
    "We then fit the BERTopic model on a collection of documents, generated topics, and returned the docs with topics.",
    "For CorEx, the topic model assumes that the input is in the form of a docword matrix, where rows represent documents and columns represent binary counts."
  ]
}